                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-231-off1230 t18270531-231-cd1231"></join>, 1 table, value 16s.; 1 bed-cover, value 1s. 6d.; 2 blankets, value 2s.; 1 coat, value 5s.; 1 waistcoat, value 2s.; 1 shirt, value 2s.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 1 comforter, value 9d.; 1 pair of stockings, value 1s., and 1 jacket, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18270531-231-victim1280" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Lewin
               <interp inst="t18270531-231-victim1280" type="surname" value="Lewin"></interp>
